text: KEAU (104.7 FM) is a radio station licensed to serve the community of Elko, Nevada. The station is owned by Elko Broadcasting Company. It airs a sports radio format, with programming from Fox Sports Radio. The station was assigned the KEAU call letters by the Federal Communications Commission on September 12, 2014. ==References== ==External links== * Official Website * EAU (FM) Category:Radio stations established in 2016 Category:2016 establishments in Nevada Category:Sports radio stations in the United States Category:Fox Sports Radio stations Category:Elko County, Nevada
